                     <title key="work_13967" type="desc">Prayers, hymns, and meditations</title>
                     <note>Texts are mainly addressed to the Virgin or Christ</note> 
                        <note>Among them are 'Lamentatio... Virginis Marie de morte... Filij' in Italian; 
                        a kind of miracle play (fol. 6v), and a similar one in Italian verse about the Passion (fol. 17)</note>
                     <note>At fol. 33 is an Italian hymn in which every line begins with 'Ama Ihesum.'
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="it" otherLangs="la">Italian and Latin</textLang>
